title: Match History not loading on website

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: Pro game not loading any of my matches that i try to look at online will not load either, anyone else having this problem.

replies.body: Everything loaded fine for me!  Are you using any extensions that could be blocking it?  You could have a caching issue as well, so I recommend starting with [clearing your cache ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)as your first step.  You can also try Incognito or another browser to see if that could work.  Hope that helps!
I've deleted my cache, as well as trying incognito and other browsers. The only extensions i could think of would be ad blocker, but i also disabled that and tried reloading it with no success.
